description: Cook time depends on thickness of breast.
name: Thawed Chicken Breast

description: Wash and dry potato. Rub potato with Canola oil and sprinkle with salt before cooking
name: Baked Potato
Frozen Chicken Nuggets
description: Lay nuggets out in a single layer. Flip after 8 minutes.

name: Fresh Potato Wedges
description: Wash potatoes and cut into wedges. Place potatoes into cold water and let sit for 30 minutes. Drain and dry. Cook in air fryer, stirring twice. After cooking, place in bowl and sprinkle with spices such as seasoning salt.

name: Frozen French Fries
description: Toss fries with seasoning salt, if desired and cook on a single layer.

name: Crispy Fresh Brussel Sprouts
description: Place brussel sprouts in bowl and microwave with 1/4 cup water, covered, for 3 minutes. Drain off water toss with olivie oil, garlic powder, onion powder and salt. Cook in air fryer.

name: Frozen Fish Sticks
description: Lay fish sticks out in a single layer. Flip after 8 minutes.
